Package: gdpins
Title: Google Drive + pins Data Management for R Projects
Version: 0.0.0.9005
Authors@R:
    person("Eduard", "Bukin", email = "ebukin@worldbank.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Layers three storage models over Google Drive: versioned pins boards
    for processed data (data-raw, data-interm, data-clean, output-tables), a
    plain-file raw-exogenous connection for API/source data, and a local-first
    output layer. All Drive access is lazy-authenticated, offline-aware,
    sync-explicit, and delete-guarded.
